1.0.name: wordpress/ios-icons-for-wordpress
1.0.description: iOS icons for Wordpress allows an image to be uploaded and properly set as an iPhone, iPod Touch or iPad icon. The icon and the icon text gets automatically defined when "Add to Home Screen" is used on the device when bookmarking the website. The demonstrated gloss effect can be applied or removed. An essential tool for mobile accessible websites or WebApps!
